(2) The funds of the Scheme shall consist of— (a) the fund of the existing fund ; (b) the assets of the existing fund ; (c) the combined contributions of contributing employers and members determined by, statutory instrument, in accordance with actuarial valuation and paid into the Scheme ; (d) income and capital appreciation derived from the holding of the assets of the Scheme in any form; and (e) such other moneys or assets as may accrue to the Scheme .
