There shall be charged on, and discharged from, the liquid assets of the Scheme —
(a) the payment of benefits in accordance with the provisions of this Act;
the payment of benefits in accordance with the provisions of this Act;
(b) the whole of the expenses incurred in connection with or incidental to the management and administration of the Scheme , including the cost of staff and the audit and actuarial investigations of the Scheme ;
